  <brief_title>The Effect of PAP on ISSHL Comorbided With OSA</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Positive Airway Pressure on Idiopathic Sudden Sensorineural Hearing Loss Comorbided With Obstructive Sleep Apnea: A Clinical Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
