  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical randomized controlled study is to explore the effect of positive airway
      pressure(PAP) on patients in Beijing Tsinghua Changgung Hospital diagnosed with both
      idiopathic sudden sensorineural hearing loss comorbided(ISSHL) and obstructive sleep
      apnea(OSA) between Dec. 2019 to Dec. 2029.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
